longBusinessSummary: Iona Energy Inc. evaluates, acquires, explores, and develops oil and gas properties in the United Kingdom's North Sea and Alaska. The company holds interests in four crude oil development projects, including Huntington, Orlando, Kells, and West Wick; and Trent & Tyne, a natural gas development project. Iona Energy Inc. is based in Calgary, Canada.
